The Aeronauts (The Epic of Flight)
Time Life Books | 1981 | ISBN: 0809432684 | PDF | 184 pages | 32.9 MB


The concept of a sky filled with balloons has intrigued people of every age and nationality for almost two centuries, ever sine men embarked on their first light-than-air voyages in 1783. From home-made air filled experiments to the "Barrage Balloons" of the war, there is plenty to intrigue young and old
